16 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
17 Article – Economic Development
18 10–519.1.
19 (a) (1) In this section the following words have the meanings indicated.
20 (2) “Eligible seafood processing project” means a project to establish or
21 expand the business of a licensed seafood dealer that:
22 (i) supports the goal of increasing the amount of oyster shells
23 retained in the State and returned to the Chesapeake Bay; and
